  {
    "id": "feat:balm-of-the-summer-court",
    "class": "subclass:circle-of-dreams",
    "level": 2,
    "name": "Balm of the Summer Court",
    "description": "You become imbued with the blessings of the Summer Court. You are a font of energy that offers respite from injuries. You have a pool of fey energy represented by a number of d6s equal to your druid level. As a bonus action, you can choose one creature you can see within 120 feet of you and spend a number of those dice equal to half your druid level or fewer. Roll the spent dice and add them together. The target regains a number of hit points equal to the total. The target also gains 1 temporary hit point per die spent. You regain all expended dice when you finish a long rest.",
